information: tropextrakt GmbH is based in Frankfurt, Germany. Since 2002, it is specialised in the import and distribution of exotic fruits. Tropextrakt now supplies 29 European countries with fruits' juice concentrates, liquid extracts, powders, HPP, purees, and other varieties. The customers for the raw materials are primarily the beverage industry. Tropextrakt also works with milk-processing companies, the confectionery industry, and manufacturers of food supplements. In addition, the internal team develops new beverage and food creations. The "Idea Lab" follow its own ideas to make new products, and also works at the request of specific customers and startups.
